<span id="freeTextContainer4047459274710409822">Not what I expected. Not at all. But that is in the most positive way. Interracial stories are normally much alike each other but this one surprised me. I liked it a lot. Well written story with a nice storyline and plot. I like that the characters and how they develop.<br/>A passionate and emotional read with twists. Enjoyable and recommendable.<br/><br/>It is a story about a white woman and a black man. They have to go through a lot before they can have their HEA. I really liked to follow them on their journ</span>
  <span id="freeText4047459274710409822" style="display:none">Not what I expected. Not at all. But that is in the most positive way. Interracial stories are normally much alike each other but this one surprised me. I liked it a lot. Well written story with a nice storyline and plot. I like that the characters and how they develop.<br />A passionate and emotional read with twists. Enjoyable and recommendable.<br /><br />It is a story about a white woman and a black man. They have to go through a lot before they can have their HEA. I really liked to follow them on their journey. They had to struggle and fight through a lot just to have a life together.<br />There are passion, drama, danger, protectiveness, betrayal, emotions and lots of chemistry in this amazing story.<br /><br />This story is written in such a captivating writing style that when I had finished it I was overwhelmed by feelings and thoughts. Absolutely an author I will come back to.<br /><br /></span>
